{"questionId":"14838180","questionHtml":"<p>Find the value of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi></math> and the value of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong> A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>attempt at ‘long division’ on&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>14</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>24</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>14</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>24</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfrac></math></strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfrac><mn>17</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mfenced><mrow><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mo>…</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; (A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>17</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>Note: </strong>Accept&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>y</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfrac><mn>17</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD 2</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong> A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>14</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>24</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>≡</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>c</mi><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>14</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>24</mn><mo>≡</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>x</mi><mfenced><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>b</mi><mfenced><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>c</mi></math></strong></em></p>\n<p>attempt to equate coefficients of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math>:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong> (M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>-</mo><mn>14</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi></math></strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>17</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>Note: </strong>Accept&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>y</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfrac><mn>17</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD 3</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong> A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>14</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>24</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>x</mi><mo>≡</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>17</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>24</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>attempt to find the limit of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></math>&nbsp;as&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>→</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>∞</mo></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><munder><mi>lim</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mo>∞</mo></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>17</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>24</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfrac></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>17</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Accept&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>y</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>x</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfrac><mn>17</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em><strong>[4 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"14838180","referenceCode":"23N.2.AHL.TZ1.11c","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Find the value of a and the value of b.","paper":"2","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"c","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 4]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 2—Functions","Topic 2—Functions","SL 2.2—Functions, notation domain, range and inverse as reflection","Topic 2—Functions","AHL 2.13—Rational functions","Topic 2—Functions","AHL 2.15—Solutions of inequalities"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}